<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'htmlhost — Disposable HTML hosting for AI agents' }) %>
  <style>
    .nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-3);
      padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .nav .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); margin-right: auto; }
    .nav .brand-mark { width: 18px; height: 18px; background: var(--text); }
    .nav .brand-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .nav .actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); }

    main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-5); }

    .hero {
      padding: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-7);
      max-width: 760px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-soft);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    }
    .eyebrow .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }
    h1.hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 60px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    }
    h1.hero-title em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }
    .hero-cta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-2); }

    .demo {
      margin: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-7);
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .demo-bar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);
      padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    .demo-bar .dot-r { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ff5f57; }
    .demo-bar .dot-y { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #febc2e; }
    .demo-bar .dot-g { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #28c840; }
    .demo-bar .label { margin-left: auto; }
    .demo pre {
      padding: var(--space-4);
      font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .demo pre .c { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .demo pre .k { color: var(--accent); }
    .demo pre .o { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .demo pre .v { color: #16a34a; }
    [data-theme="dark"] .demo pre .v { color: #4ade80; }
    .demo pre .arrow { color: var(--text-muted); }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
    }
    .feature {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: var(--space-5);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-2);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    .feature-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
    .feature h3 {
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .feature p {
      font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .pitch {
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-elevated);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
    }
    .pitch-text {
      font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.6;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .pitch-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
    .pitch-text em { color: var(--text-muted); font-style: normal; }

    .sketch {
      padding: var(--space-7) 0 var(--space-8);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .sketch h2 {
      font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    .sketch p.lead {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    }
    .sketch .step-list {
      display: grid; gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .step {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
      background: var(--bg);
    }
    .step-num {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-subtle);
      padding-top: 2px;
    }
    .step-body strong { display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .step-body span { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 13px; }

    .cta-band {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-4);
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: var(--space-6);
      background: var(--bg-elevated);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
    }
    .cta-band h3 {
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      max-width: 460px;
    }
    .cta-band .actions { display: flex; gap: var(--space-2); flex-wrap: wrap; }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-6);
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding-left: var(--space-5); padding-right: var(--space-5);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-4);
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    footer .links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); margin-right: auto; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav, main, footer { padding-left: var(--space-3); padding-right: var(--space-3); }
      .hero { padding-top: var(--space-7); }
      h1.hero-title { font-size: 36px; }
      .hero-sub { font-size: 16px; }
      .step { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-2); }
      footer { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/" class="brand">
      <div class="brand-mark"></div>
      <div class="brand-name">htmlhost</div>
    </a>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn btn-sm" href="https://github.com/sebas-developer/htmlhost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38v-1.34c-2.22.48-2.69-1.07-2.69-1.07-.36-.92-.89-1.16-.89-1.16-.73-.5.06-.49.06-.49.8.06 1.23.83 1.23.83.71 1.22 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.13 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82a7.65 7.65 0 0 1 4 0c1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.11.16 1.93.08 2.13.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48v2.19c0 .21.15.46.55.38A8 8 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
      <button class="icon-btn" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle theme" data-theme-icon></button>
      <a class="btn btn-sm" href="/login">Sign in</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        Built for agents
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Disposable HTML hosting <em>for AI agents.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Upload → random URL → self-destructs. A single CLI, a 12-word mnemonic,
        zero dashboards to babysit. <strong>Give your agent one skill file and
        it ships HTML to the web in one command.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://github.com/sebas-developer/htmlhost#install-the-skill-agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Get the skill
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-lg" href="/login">Sign in</a>
      </div>

      <div class="demo">
        <div class="demo-bar">
          <span class="dot-r"></span><span class="dot-y"></span><span class="dot-g"></span>
          <span class="label">terminal</span>
        </div>
<pre><span class="c"># your agent, in one command</span>
<span class="k">$</span> htmlhost upload landing-page.html <span class="k">--ttl</span> 7d
<span class="v">  Uploaded: vcc6Q2Fb</span>
<span class="v">  URL: https://html-host.fly.dev/p/vcc6Q2Fb</span>
<span class="v">  Expires: 7d</span>

<span class="c"># with an image — assets live under the paste</span>
<span class="k">$</span> htmlhost asset vcc6Q2Fb ./hero.png <span class="k">--path</span> hero.png
<span class="v">  Uploaded: https://html-host.fly.dev/a/vcc6Q2Fb/hero.png</span>
<span class="v">  Size: 290.4KB   Type: image/png</span>

<span class="c"># paste lives 7 days, then deletes itself. no cleanup.</span></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pitch">
      <p class="pitch-text">
        The whole product is the loop: <strong>an agent generates HTML,
        hosts it, and hands you a URL</strong> — without breaking flow. No
        build step. No git. No deploy pipeline. <em>The page lives as long
        as you tell it to, then it's gone.</em>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 16V4M12 4l-4 4M12 4l4 4"/><path d="M4 14v4a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>One-shot hosting</h3>
        <p>One command, one URL. No accounts to click through, no dashboards to babysit, no deploy pipeline to wire up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Ephemeral by default</h3>
        <p>TTL from 1 hour to indefinite. Demos, previews, and throwaways self-destruct — no cleanup duty, no orphan pages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/><path d="M4 14l4-4 4 4 4-4 4 4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Assets, not just HTML</h3>
        <p>Drop images, audio, fonts, video, CSS, JS, PDFs under a paste and reference them by absolute URL. A full static site, not a single file.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Mnemonic auth, no passwords</h3>
        <p>One 12-word phrase derives the API key. Nothing to paste into a browser, nothing to leak in a screenshot. Server stores only a hash.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 014 4v3H8V6a4 4 0 014-4z"/><rect x="4" y="9" width="16" height="13" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="15" r="1.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Agent-native skill</h3>
        <p>A single <code>SKILL.md</code> teaches OpenCode, Claude Code, and Codex the full lifecycle — install, auth, upload, asset handling, the relative-path trap.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 12l3-3 3 3 5-5 4 4 3-3"/><path d="M3 21h18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Self-hostable</h3>
        <p>Single Node service, SQLite on a volume, deploys to fly.io or Docker in minutes. Your data, your rules, your access key.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sketch">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <p class="lead">Drop one skill file into your agent's skills directory. From there, the loop is a single conversation.</p>
      <div class="step-list">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Install the skill</strong>
            <span>One curl to <code>~/.config/opencode/skills/</code>, <code>~/.claude/skills/</code>, or <code>~/.agents/skills/</code>.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Ask your agent to host something</strong>
            <span>"Upload this HTML page" — the agent runs <code>htmlhost setup</code> on first call, generates a 12-word mnemonic, saves credentials to <code>~/.htmlhost/config.json</code>.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Get a URL</strong>
            <span>The agent uploads, references assets by absolute URL, and reports the final paste URL back. Page lives as long as you told it to, then deletes itself.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-band">
      <h3>Give your agent one skill file. It handles the rest.</h3>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/sebas-developer/htmlhost#install-the-skill-agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Install the skill
        </a>
        <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/sebas-developer/htmlhost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/sebas-developer/htmlhost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      <a href="/login">Sign in</a>
      <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/pastes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">API</a>
    </div>
    <span>htmlhost · MIT</span>
  </footer>

  <%- include('partials/theme') %>
</body>
</html>
